media:group.media:title: Acentos Bienvenidos: Con Café | Lunch | The Disney Bundle
media:group.media:description:
Sit down with Ramon Guzman and Anthony “Chorizo” Nguyen (The Crazy Gorilla), Jenny Lorenzo (Disney+), Rebeca Huntt (Beba, Hulu), and Katia Castorena (Journalist, ESPN+ Deportes) as they talk about identity, cultura, and familia over a cafecito. To see more of their work, check out Jenny on What’s Up Disney+, Katia on ESPN+ Deportes and Rebeca
Huntt on Hulu for her new film Beba. #AcentosBienvenidos #DisneyBundle
